Name: OSC Cam Type
LongName: Current OSC CAM profile selected; Aggressive(AGRES), Harmonic(HARMON), Trapezoidal (TRAPEZ)

Name: Load Next Program
LongName: Defines Weld program link mode to automatically link next program after defined repeated programs, (YES/NO option)

Name: Change Head at the end
LongName: Defines whether to swap head or not after program complete, (YES/NO option)

Name: AVC Type
LongName: Current ARC mode; Continuos(Cont), Background Lock (Bck Lock), Foreground Lock(Frg Lock), Locked(Lock)

Name: Relation between WF and WP
LongName: Defines mode to ratio wire pulse speed to wire feed speed, (YES/NO option),

Name: TVL Calib. Mode
LongName: TVL Calib. Mode : wit Arc Start or Load Bank
